Version 0.0.4 - Wed 06 Jun 2001

    * Dirty rectangle support.
    * General code cleanup.

Version 0.0.3 - Wed 23 Aug 2000

	* Deep project architecture.
	* Long command line options.
	* Command console buttons.
	* Proportional console font.
	* Abstract hexagonal math.
	* Hex LOS and range display.
	* Radar sector grid.

Version 0.0.2 - Wed 28 Jun 2000

	* Hex coordinate display.
	* Simple bitmap font.
	* Console status bar display.
	* Class hierarchy cleanup.
	* Window resizing.
	* RLE accelerated blits.

Version 0.0.1 - Tue 18 Apr 2000

	* Preliminary GUI windowing system.
	* Nonrectangular command console.
	* Color mouse cursor.
	* Mouse scrolling in radar view.
	* Input grabbing.
	* Window iconification.

Version 0.0.0 - Thu 30 Dec 1999

	* Fractal map generator.
	* 2-axis rotary buffer scrolling.
	* Scrolling radar view.
	* Clear and water base tiles.
	* Light and heavy woods fringe tiles.
	* Grid display and 3-level zooming.
